# Module headers (required)

## Standard

Follow `docs/ai/module-headers.md`.

Required YAML keys:

- `module` (prefix must match `docs/ai/module-map.yml`)
- `purpose` (1â€“2 sentences)
- `exports` (public entrypoints / outputs / commands)
- `patterns` (required patterns used here)

## Wrappers by file type (first non-empty content)

- `*.bicep`, `*.bicepparam`, `*.cs`, `*.ts`, `*.tsx`: `/* ... */`
- `*.ps1`, `*.psm1`: `<# ... #>`
- `*.vue`, `*.md`: `<!-- ... -->`
- `*.sql`: `-- ` prefixed YAML lines
- `*.yml`, `*.yaml`: `# ` prefixed YAML lines

## Special case: `.mdc` and `SKILL.md`

Rules and skills must start with YAML frontmatter. Include the module header keys inside the same frontmatter block (do not add a second header).

